  "detailed_description": "Kuro Neko is a 2D platformer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn Kuro Neko you have got lost and you must find your way home by collecting oil lanterns and avoiding monsters. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 4 player battle you see who can survive until the end.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControls:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayer 1:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLeft: A Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRight: D Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJump: Space BAr<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayer 2:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLeft: Left  Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRight: Right Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJump: N Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayer 3:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLeft:  G Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRight: J Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJump: O Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayer 4:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLeft: 4 Num Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRight: 6 Num Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJump: PG Up Key<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSingle Player also works with an Xbox Controller",
